183/*******************************************************************************
184 * PGRAPH context implementation
185 ******************************************************************************/
186
187void
188gf117_grctx_generate_attrib(struct gf100_grctx *info)
189{
190 struct gf100_gr *gr = info->gr;
191 const struct gf100_grctx_func *grctx = gr->func->grctx;
192 const u32 alpha = grctx->alpha_nr;
193 const u32 beta = grctx->attrib_nr;
194 const u32 size = 0x20 * (grctx->attrib_nr_max + grctx->alpha_nr_max);
195 const u32 access = NV_MEM_ACCESS_RW;
196 const int s = 12;
197 const int b = mmio_vram(info, size * gr->tpc_total, (1 << s), access);
198 const int timeslice_mode = 1;
199 const int max_batches = 0xffff;
200 u32 bo = 0;
201 u32 ao = bo + grctx->attrib_nr_max * gr->tpc_total;
202 int gpc, ppc;
203
204 mmio_refn(info, 0x418810, 0x80000000, s, b);
205 mmio_refn(info, 0x419848, 0x10000000, s, b);
206 mmio_wr32(info, 0x405830, (beta << 16) | alpha);
207 mmio_wr32(info, 0x4064c4, ((alpha / 4) << 16) | max_batches);
208
209 for (gpc = 0; gpc < gr->gpc_nr; gpc++) {
210 for (ppc = 0; ppc < gr->ppc_nr[gpc]; ppc++) {
211 const u32 a = alpha * gr->ppc_tpc_nr[gpc][ppc];
212 const u32 b = beta * gr->ppc_tpc_nr[gpc][ppc];
213 const u32 t = timeslice_mode;
214 const u32 o = PPC_UNIT(gpc, ppc, 0);
215 if (!(gr->ppc_mask[gpc] & (1 << ppc)))
216 continue;
217 mmio_skip(info, o + 0xc0, (t << 28) | (b << 16) | ++bo);
218 mmio_wr32(info, o + 0xc0, (t << 28) | (b << 16) | --bo);
219 bo += grctx->attrib_nr_max * gr->ppc_tpc_nr[gpc][ppc];
220 mmio_wr32(info, o + 0xe4, (a << 16) | ao);
221 ao += grctx->alpha_nr_max * gr->ppc_tpc_nr[gpc][ppc];
222 }
223 }
224}
225
226static void
227gf117_grctx_generate_main(struct gf100_gr *gr, struct gf100_grctx *info)
228{
229 struct nvkm_device *device = gr->base.engine.subdev.device;
230 const struct gf100_grctx_func *grctx = gr->func->grctx;
231 int i;
232
233 nvkm_mc_unk260(device->mc, 0);
234
235 gf100_gr_mmio(gr, grctx->hub);
236 gf100_gr_mmio(gr, grctx->gpc);
237 gf100_gr_mmio(gr, grctx->zcull);
238 gf100_gr_mmio(gr, grctx->tpc);
239 gf100_gr_mmio(gr, grctx->ppc);
240
241 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404154, 0x00000000);
242
243 grctx->bundle(info);
244 grctx->pagepool(info);
245 grctx->attrib(info);
246 grctx->unkn(gr);
247
248 gf100_grctx_generate_tpcid(gr);
249 gf100_grctx_generate_r406028(gr);
250 gf100_grctx_generate_r4060a8(gr);
251 gk104_grctx_generate_r418bb8(gr);
252 gf100_grctx_generate_r406800(gr);
253
254 for (i = 0; i < 8; i++)
255 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x4064d0 + (i * 0x04), 0x00000000);
256
257 gf100_gr_icmd(gr, grctx->icmd);
258 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404154, 0x00000400);
259 gf100_gr_mthd(gr, grctx->mthd);
260 nvkm_mc_unk260(device->mc, 1);
261}
262
263const struct gf100_grctx_func
264gf117_grctx = {
265 .main = gf117_grctx_generate_main,
266 .unkn = gk104_grctx_generate_unkn,
267 .hub = gf117_grctx_pack_hub,
268 .gpc = gf117_grctx_pack_gpc,
269 .zcull = gf100_grctx_pack_zcull,
270 .tpc = gf117_grctx_pack_tpc,
271 .ppc = gf117_grctx_pack_ppc,
272 .icmd = gf119_grctx_pack_icmd,
273 .mthd = gf119_grctx_pack_mthd,
274 .bundle = gf100_grctx_generate_bundle,
275 .bundle_size = 0x1800,
276 .pagepool = gf100_grctx_generate_pagepool,
277 .pagepool_size = 0x8000,
278 .attrib = gf117_grctx_generate_attrib,
279 .attrib_nr_max = 0x324,
280 .attrib_nr = 0x218,
281 .alpha_nr_max = 0x7ff,
282 .alpha_nr = 0x324,
283};
